summary: Adds a house made for a ranger character on the small island in riverwood in front of the lumbermill.
descriptionHtml:
This is my fist mod for skyrim and i wanted to upload it.

It adds a small farmhouse just in front of the lumbermill in riverwood. you can acces the house right away without any quests.
The house contains: 2 mannequins, 4 places on a weapon rack, a small weapon rack above your bed and a cooking spit near the fireplace.
also all empty chests wont respawn any other container will

Installation: extract the zip file into your data folder, after that start skyrim and click data files and activate the esp file.
Uninstallation: deactivate or delete the esp file all should be fine and the riverwood erea is returned to normal.

Credits:
Blary for his food crates mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=14133

Version history:

version 3.1:

-removed log at back of house
-added an archery target
-added basement

version 2.1:
edited navmesh inside the house, bug with followers not know how to walk down stairs fixed.
dragons can now land on top of the house.
removed chair from fire outside (didnt like it)

version 2.0:
added navmeshes inside and outside the house.
added fire outside the house with benches.
added a target for bow practice outside the house
